Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A shy lantern blinked three times from\Nbehind a tree near a tiny penguin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In the seaside dune, the penguin learned that a cloud\Nhad misplaced the silver bell that guided it home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What began as a rescue mission grew harder\Nwhen the paper star slipped out of reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The thoughtful penguin decided to reach the stranded friend and\Nfollowed the clues and arranged bright stones into an arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.00,0:00:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan worked, bringing a safe rescue\Nfor everyone in the seaside dune.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The new friends celebrated with a tiny dance under the leaves.\NThe paper star softly echoed the adventure's beginning.
